# LogPatternScope - Repetition & Spike Analyzer

LogPatternScope surfaces high-frequency log lines and can detect sudden anomalies in system or app logs.

## Features
- Burst detection  
- Keyword flagging  
- Frequency heatmap  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/34_LogPatternScope.git
cd 34_LogPatternScope
python analyze.py
